I'm a beast. I'm a beast.

133
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,760
- Dad.
- I'm a beast.

134
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:58,960
Mom.

135
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:06,120
Dad.

136
