195
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,880
We'll have a meeting after the meal.

196
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:24,480
Alright.

197
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:33,120
Want chili?

198
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,080
Yes, please.

199
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:36,000
