It's ready, it's ready.

203
00:12:41,260 --> 00:12:42,120
This one's yours.

204
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,160
Okay, thanks.

205
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:47,440
Don't go! Her beef isn't fresh.

206
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,720
- It's sour.
- Smell it.

207
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,160
- It's spoiled.
- I buy from her all the time.

208
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,440
This is freshly bought beef!

209
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,440
Fresh beef?

210
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,920
How long did you have it
before selling it to us?

211
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:55,400
Don't buy it, everyone! Get a refund!

212
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:57,000
- What are you doing? Refund!
- Refund!

213
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,360
Hurry up and refund us!

214
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,720
I don't want it.

215
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,520
Give the refund! Hurry up!

216
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,460
What are you staring at?

217
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,720
Qiaoqiao, are you hungry?

218
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,800
Qiaoqiao?

219
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:17,520
Qiaoqiao?

220
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,440
Sir, have you seen Qiaoqiao?

221
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,680
No.

222
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,910
Qiaoqiao!

223
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:24,210
Qiaoqiao!

224
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:25,160
Qiaoqiao!

225
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:27,800
Have you seen Qiaoqiao?

226
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,680
Have you seen a little girl?

227
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:30,680
Officer.

228
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:33,200
Officer, my child is missing.

229
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,280
I can't find my child.

230
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,520
I can't find my child.

231
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:36,560
Take it easy.

232
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:38,200
Calm down and tell us what happened.

233
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,360
She's about three years old.

234
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,520
About this tall.

235
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,600
Wearing pink clothes

236
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,520
with a ponytail.

237
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:43,800
But I can't find her.

238
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:45,560
I've searched several streets already.

239
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:46,400
We got it.

240
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,920
We'll help you find her, don't worry.

241
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:49,210
Captain Ye.

242
00:13:49,210 --> 00:13:50,780
The child isn't crying or fussing.

243
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:52,110
Suspect likely be an acquaintance.

244
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:55,560
I've already sent the suspect's video.

245
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,120
Take a look.

246
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,840
Do you recognize this person?

247
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:01,960
Yes, I do.

248
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,640
He's the eldest brother in our family.

249
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,720
He doesn't have children.

250
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:11,480
He just likes playing with Qiaoqiao.

251
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:14,480
