281
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:43,480
Take it out.

282
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:45,920
Take it out!

283
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:03,760
Name?

284
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:07,800
Liu Dachuan.

285
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,960
You were the one who put drugs

286
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:12,120
